&gt; happenings.  Lots of &quot;demons&quot; (they have Lorraine Warren guest all 
the
&gt; time), and they usually try to do investigations/ communication only
&gt; during what they call &quot;dead time&quot;, 3am-4am, or &quot;the polar opposite 
of
&gt; 3pm - the time Jesus gave is life for all mankind&quot; as they put it. 
Oh,
&gt; and they have an &quot;occult specialist&quot; on the team that so far has 
been
&gt; anything but.
&gt; 
&gt; On the positive side, they did actually get (and record for later
&gt; analysis) live communication on the box in response to questions 
being
&gt; asked.  And on the analysis and isolation of the recorded parts, you
&gt; could actually hear what was being said (as opposed to the usual of
&gt; Chris acting as a go-between for very distorted sounds like on those
&gt; youtube videos).  So it was good to see it a)working in the &quot;field&quot;
&gt; and b)get some exposure on a tv show.
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; Marty
